Hi!

I’m Berry, a freelance R trainer and consultant based in Potsdam, Germany.
I give R courses, develop rdwd and other packages and co-organize the Berlin R User Group.

Contact me to book me as a trainer or request assistance with data science projects.

Packages on CRAN
